text":"Paradoja obesidad → grasa infiltrada ↑ riesgo fx aunque DMO normal","guid":"jn2tAKAwDE2ZOyxkpE3xJA","children":[]},{"id":"206","parent":"197","text":"DENOSUMAB NUNCA suspender sin traslape → rebote fx multiples","guid":"H4xFxww5WE6tWTeNxDmKcA","children":[]},{"id":"207","parent":"197","text":"CORTICOIDES causa secundaria MAS AGRESIVA → prevencion 5mg+ x 3m+","guid":"mAHLRhOcxUyGBSuwWo8Ucg","children":[]},{"id":"208","parent":"197","text":"Screening DXA debe incluir masa muscular cuerpo completo","guid":"hA_59UZImUW6WC4L_b9GhQ","children":[]},{"id":"209","parent":"197","text":"MNA bajo en osteosarcopenico → nutricion PRIORIDAD","guid":"sWPvD2ij2kOyVMEOtrX3zA","children":[]},{"id":"210","parent":"197","text":"EJERCICIO RESISTENCIA beneficia AMBOS compartimentos","guid":"9x6JHS4PbU2NnV_eX4pecg","children":[]},{"id":"211","parent":"197","text":"PTH alta SIN deficit vitD ni falla renal → buscar osteosarcopenia","guid":"CKhXTKSAQkO3ixsWEK-s0g","children":[]},{"id":"212","parent":"197","text":"Sarcopenia SEVERA en osteosarcopenico → amplifica riesgo OR mayor3","guid":"77y04I3XL0u2sactcuCKZQ","children":[]},{"id":"213","parent":"197","text":"Farmacos sarcopenia aislados FRACASARON → target incorrecto?","guid":"VlGOrUw6yE6jjwMhpp6-Wg","children":[]},{"id":"214","parent":"197","text":"D3-creatina dilucion → mejor predictor outcomes que DXA","guid":"LcrKF9QQL0KhZFDH6IaBMw","children":[]},{"id":"215","parent":"197","text":"Caidas en geriatricos → pensar sarcopenia 21% mayor65a","guid":"7eRCjaXpLEKTICOs0gqyhQ","children":[]},{"id":"216","parent":"197","text":"SARC-F preguntar creativamente bidon 5L perrito bolsa supermercado","guid":"AnjwzoT-LkmVIlmMfotGhw","children":[]},{"id":"217","parent":"197","text":"Denosumab → unico farmaco con senal beneficio muscular ↓ caidas","guid":"BMEpD-CPc0qYbqy_lWWXgQ","children":[]},{"id":"218","parent":"197","text":"Proteinas FRACCIONADAS durante dia → por resistencia anabolica","guid":"jN8deCa850ehXFqqSZOknA","children":[]},{"id":"219",